1. *Zaustavila* je automobil na semaforu. (She stopped the car at the traffic light.) 
2. *Zaustavljali* smo se po cesti da bi proverili mapu. (We were stopping along the road to check the map.) 
3. Ona je *zaustavila* svoje dete da ne bi izašlo na ulicu. (She stopped her child so it wouldn't go out on the street.) 
4. *Zaustavio* sam ga da ne bi otišao dalje. (I stopped him so he wouldn't go further.) 
5. Policija je *zaustavila* automobil kako bi proverila dokumenta. (The police stopped the car to check the documents.) 
6. *Zaustavljala* sam se svakih nekoliko minuta da bi odmorila. (I was stopping every few minutes to take a rest.)